OL,4,CStudents: 'Uni definitely not good
OL,5,Cvalue this year'
OL,6, Only about a quarter of students in the
OL,7, UK thought they got good value for
OL,8, money from university in the pandemic.
OL,10,FAn annual survey found students felt
OL,11,Ftheir fees and living costs were not
OL,12,Fjustified by the disrupted teaching
OL,13,Fthey received this academic year.
OL,15,FStudents were particularly aggrieved by
OL,16,Fa lack of in-person teaching, found the
OL,17,Fsurvey of 10,000 students from the
OL,18,FHigher Education Policy Institute.
OL,20,FUniversities UK said the results were
OL,21,F"disappointing, albeit not surprising".
